item.title: far too late
item.description: i’m writing this at 5:44 am, i’ve been awake this whole time coding stuff for this website but now i just felt like writing this blog post. there’s no point cause no one knows about this or reads this, but whatever. i listened to reol, imperial circus dead decadence, cö shu nie and some other stuff spotify autoplayed, was fun. tomorrow is friday though so i still have to sleep now.
